request.description:
Get task statistics by status

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "total": 25,
    "pending": 10,
    "inProgress": 5,
    "completed": 10
  }
}
```

Get paginated task list with advanced filtering

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "tasks": [...],
    "pagination": {
      "page": 1,
      "limit": 10,
      "total": 45,
      "totalPages": 5
    }
  }
}
```

✅ CORRECTED - Get all subtasks for a specific task

**Backend Route**: GET /v1/tasks/subtask/task/:taskId

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "_subTaskId": "sub123",
      "title": "Step 1",
      "isCompleted": false,
      "order": 1
    }
  ]
}
```

✅ NEW - Get paginated subtasks for a task

**Backend Route**: GET /v1/tasks/subtask/task/:taskId/paginate

**Use Case**: When task has 100+ subtasks

**Response**:
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "subtasks": [...],
    "pagination": {
      "page": 1,
      "limit": 10,
      "total": 150,
      "totalPages": 15
    }
  }
}
```
